                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a standard action, the pickpocket can attempt a Sleight of Hand check (DC 20 + the target\u2019s level or CR) in combat to snatch a small, non-held item from a target, disguising it as a feint or dodge. On a success, the pickpocket takes the item and quickly conceals it on their person. The target can attempt an opposed Perception check against the pickpocket\u2019s Sleight of Hand result to notice the theft.",
